<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>list user | New Coding</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:200,300,400,600,700,800" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #071117;
      --panel: rgba(12, 24, 34, 0.84);
      --line: rgba(147, 184, 205, 0.16);
      --text: #eef9ff;
      --muted: #91aaba;
      --accent: #89f4d8;
      --warm: #ffc775;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(137, 244, 216, 0.15), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #04080d 0%, #09151d 36%, #0b1f2c 100%);
    }
    .page {
      width: min(1240px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 26px 0 56px;
    }
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(4, 14, 21, 0.64);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .brand img {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .nav a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      text-transform: lowercase;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    .nav a.active,
    .nav a:hover {
      border-color: var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }
    .hero, .table-shell {
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--panel);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }
    .hero {
      padding: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 22px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(137, 244, 216, 0.1);
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin: 0;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 18px;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.4rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }
    p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .hero-side {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .hero-side article {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .table-shell {
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .table-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 24px 24px 0;
    }
    .count {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #00f2c3;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .table-wrap {
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      min-width: 980px;
    }
    th, td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 16px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      vertical-align: top;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    th {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <img src="https://pixhost.to/show/7353/717289326_img-20260422-wa0016.jpg" alt="New Coding">
        <span>New Coding</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/docs">dashboard</a>
        <a href="/admin/index">admin</a>
        <a href="/admin/listuser" class="active">list user</a>
        <a href="/changelog">changelog</a>
        <a href="/users/logout">logout</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">list user</span>
        <h1>lihat user lebih cepat tanpa warna yang beda sendiri.</h1>
        <p>halaman ini saya samakan ke warna panel admin utama supaya tetap nyambung saat pindah halaman.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-side">
        <article>
          <h3>yang kelihatan langsung</h3>
          <p>status akun, plan user, limit, email, dan apikey bisa dipantau tanpa scroll terlalu jauh.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>alur admin</h3>
          <p>setelah cek data user, admin bisa balik ke panel utama untuk premium, changelog, atau tautan undangan.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="table-shell">
      <div class="table-head">
        <div>
          <h2>list user</h2>
          <p>semua user yang tersimpan di database ditampilkan di bawah ini.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="count">total user: <%= List.length %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>username</th>
              <th>status</th>
              <th>plan</th>
              <th>limit</th>
              <th>email</th>
              <th>api key</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% List.forEach((item) => { %>
              <tr>
                <td><strong><%= item.username || '-' %></strong></td>
                <td>
                  <span class="pill"><%= item.status !== null ? 'active' : 'not active' %></span>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <span class="pill"><%= item.premium !== null ? 'premium user' : 'free user' %></span>
                </td>
                <td><%= item.limit ?? 0 %></td>
                <td><%= item.email || '-' %></td>
                <td><%= item.apikey || '-' %></td>
              </tr>
            <% }) %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

